OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start in the east with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain but these soon
OL,7,Fclearing. Otherwise, mainly dry and
OL,8,Fbright but a few showers will develop,
OL,9,Fthese becoming more widespread in the
OL,10,Fwest later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA bright evening in the east
OL,13,Fbut cloudier in the west with showers
OL,14,For longer spells of rain. The showers
OL,15,Fwill spread eastwards overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA largely cloudy day with
OL,18,Fbright intervals and showers. Some of
OL,19,Fthese could be heavy and thundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
